
we have 7 layers

application layer  L7
presentation layer(ssl/tsl) L6
session layer  L5
transport layer L4
network layer L3
datalink layer L2
physical layer L1 

1. ALB is Application load balancer
Layer 7
handles http requests
costly
slow response
having lot of load balancing features
EX: amazon.com virtusa.cm

2. NLB is Network loadbalancer
layer 4
stickey session
handles TCP/UDP requests
start from transport layer
low cost
fast response
EX:gaming, youtbe streaming

3. GWLD is gateway loadbalancer
very high security than ALB, NLB
to handle virtual appliances
VPN
firewall
